  </Fragment>

  <div class="call-banner">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span>Bertazzoni column acting up? Same-day service across LA:</span>
      <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="phone-lg">(424) 325-0520</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Bertazzoni › Refrigerator Repair</div>
          <h1>Bertazzoni Refrigerator Repair</h1>
          <p class="lede">
            Bertazzoni is the six-generation Italian family manufacturer from Guastalla, Emilia-Romagna — 143 years
